    <div id="slide4" class="slide">
        <div class="title">
            <h2>Advanced Ultrasound Technology</h2>
            <p>
                Our company is at the forefront of ultrasound technology. We offer a wide range of diagnostic services, including:
                <br>
                <br>
                3D and 4D Ultrasounds: Providing detailed, real-time imaging of the developing fetus, creating cherished moments for expectant parents.
                <br>
                <br>
                High-Resolution Medical Ultrasounds: Accurate and detailed images for various medical applications, from abdominal scans to cardiac evaluations.
                <br>
                <br>
                Vascular Ultrasound: Assessing blood flow and detecting vascular conditions to support informed medical decisions.
                <br>
                <br>
                Doppler Ultrasound: Evaluating blood circulation, identifying abnormalities, and guiding treatment plans.
            </p>
        </div>
